data.description: WOULDA, SHOULDA, COULDA!!  PRICED BELOW TAX VALUE! DON'T GET CAUGHT NAPPING ON THIS RARE OPPORTUNITY! Lovely spacious modular home near East Gaston High School, situated in a very convenient and desirable neighborhood. Three roomy bedrooms include a large master suite with walk-in shower and soaker tub. Roomy living room, cozy den, ample kitchen with abundant cabinets and counter space, 2 bathrooms and an attached garage. Entertain your guests or relax in the refreshing solitude and privacy of the rear decks and spacious grounds. Huge wired workshop, additional storage building. Spacious lawn ready for your personal design. A new roof will be installed and some other repairs completed prior to closing. Compare this to the overpriced box homes on POSTAGE STAMP LOTS! Show Thurs, Fri, Sat, by appt- --Sundays after 2
